&lt;C-I-L Inc> said it would exercise itsright to acquire &lt;Trimac Ltd>'s stake in their jointly ownedTricil Ltd for 91 mln dlrs, with closing expected May 22.    C-I-L added that the final price could be less, however,depending on an Ontario court ruling resulting from apreviously reported legal action launched by C-I-L.    Mississauga, Ontario-based Tricil is a waste managementcompany with operations in the U.S. and Canada. Reuter&#3;